ze-adjust: 100%;color: #262626;font-family: Georgia=2C serif;font-size: 15=
px;line-height: 175%;text-align: left;">Schopenhauer=E2=80=99s central pre=
mise is that talent achieves what others cannot achieve=2C whereas genius=
