adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #262626;font-family: Georgi=
a=2C serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 175%;text-align: left;">But the cu=
rse of the extraordinary=2C Schopenhauer suggests=2C is a certain loneline=
ss with which the person of genius walks through life=2C always slightly a=
part from the ordinary world in being slightly above it:</p><blockquote st=
yle=3D"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;display:=
